97
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:44,960
We heard that people very quickly latch onto food trends.

98
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,480
Then there was hunch.

99
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:49,680
A hunch is a feeling about something you think might be true,

100
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,879
even though you don't have real evidence for it.

101
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:57,600
ingesting something means taking it into your body, so eating or drinking it.

102
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:01,520
And finally, a stringent rule is a very strict rule.

103
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:04,799
A tough rule or law, which in connection to food,

104
00:06:04,799 --> 00:06:08,560
is designed to make sure it is safe and of a suitable quality.

105
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,759
Okay, thank you, Sam.

